| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0392 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0f6cb7b1-31b8-5de0-a3c9-7acd4e8f6c83"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
